milestones.description: Don Maxwell and Dhaniram's 70-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 31 between Codrington and Umar Bhatti
John Davison has broken the record for most catches (5) in ODIs for CAN, going past Sanjayan Thuraisingam's 4
This is the lowest match aggregate (417) involving teams Canada & Scotland in ODIs

stories.title: Blain cameo edges Scotland home
stories.subTitle: Canada v Scotland, 5th match, Tri-series, Mombasa
stories.summary: A bristling cameo of 30 from John Blain squeezed Scotland past Canada by two wickets in the fifth match of the Tri Series, following a flurry of middle-order wickets in a tense encounter at Mombasa
